<h1>2d_loops</h1>
<h3>Looping a 2 dimensional data structure (like a matrix, or table)</h3>
{% set matrix = [
    [ "English", "Spanish", "French" ],
    [ "And this one of them", "Y este es uno de ellos", "et c'est l'un d'entre eux" ],
    [ "And this is another", "Y este es otro", "Et c'est un autre" ],
    [ "And this is another", "Y este es otro", "Et c'est un autre" ],
    [ "And this is another", "Y este es otro", "Et c'est un autre" ],
    [ "And this is the last element", "Y este es el elemento final", "Et c'est le dernier élément" ]
] %}

<table>
    {% for row in matrix %}
        {# new row #}
        <tr>
            {% set rowloop = loop %}
            {% for cell in row %}

                {# Indexes start at ONE #}
                {% if rowloop.index == 1 %}
                    <th>
                        {% set columnloop = loop %}
                        {{ cell }}
                    </th>
                {% else %}
                    <td>
                        {% set columnloop = loop %}
                        {{ cell }}
                    </td>
                {% endif %}

            {% endfor %}
        </tr>
    {% endfor %}
</table>
